parameters:
Thug Henchman: At least... make it so he doesn't suffer
anymore... Ugh... Please, put my big bro out of his misery,
I beg you... uuu...
Thug Henchman: Miss... what about the boss...?
I couldn't do it...
Thug Henchman: No way...

Indeed, as you say, ensuring he doesn't suffer might be
considered an act of mercy.

But I couldn't bring myself to believe that was the right
thing to do...

Thug Henchman: For the boss to end up like that... it's just
too much...

Indeed, the result of what happened to him is unbearable to
witness.
But just the same, we mustn't give up hope.

If magic experiments have caused this, then perhaps magic
could also be the key to restoring his original form, might
it not?

Thug Henchman: But... until we find a way, the boss will
remain like that?!
You! You must believe in him!!

Is the man you deeply believe in really such a weak man? No,
that can't be right!!!

If you care about him, then you must believe! Believe in his
strength! In his tenacity to survive until now!! And in a
future where you can laugh together as comrades once more!!!
Thug Henchman: Ugh! Uuuuuh...!!

It's true, you may be villains! But this is something that
cannot be allowed! Don't succumb to misfortune! Don't just
go with the flow! Choose to live on, no matter how dirty it
gets!

Just as you have lived through everything with him until
now!

Thug Henchman: Uuuuh...!! That's right...! The boss was
dirtier and tougher than anyone...! And yet, what was I
thinking...!!

You're not at fault. Your feelings for him were just too
strong, that's all.

Thug Henchman: But... how do we find a way to return the
boss to normal...

No worries. Who do you think I am? I am Reisha, a knight
from the royal capital Near Lake. I will lend you my
strength. If we scour the capital and that's not enough,
then we'll search beyond the country's borders.

Once this matter with him is resolved, you all will properly
atone for your crimes. Once your atonement is complete, come
to me again. Let's work together to make this country
better!

Thug Henchman: Ughuuu! I'm sorry...! So sorry...!! Uuuuhhh!!
Uuuuuuhhh...!!

events.name: ごろつきイベ_はじまり

parameters: Thug Minion: Hey, you there!!

Are you one of the thugs who attacked the shop in the
reconstruction district?! Why are you here...?!

Thug Minion: I'll explain later! It's the boss! He's been
taken to the lab by the researchers here!!
What did you say?!?

Thug Minion: Please! I apologize for what happened before! I
know I have no right to ask this of you!

Thug Minion: But right now, you're the only one I can turn
to! Please!! Save my boss!!

Thug Minion: One of our guys was already used as
experimental material and got killed! No one who's taken to
that room ever comes back!!

Thug Minion: I'm begging you! Please save my boss...!!
Please!!
Damn it!! Where is that place? Tell me quickly!
Thug Minion: I think it's just down this road!!
I'm on it!

(They must have been caught by the facility's people to
silence them after escaping that scene. They may be petty
criminals, but life is precious regardless of status. If
they're asking for help, it's up to me to do something...!!)
